sequenceDiagram
    participant MLApp as ML Application
    participant OnlineServer as Feature Server Online<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    participant Registry as Registry Service<br/>6570/TCP gRPC
    participant OnlineDB as Online Store<br/>Redis/PostgreSQL<br/>6379/5432 TCP
    participant Transform as Transformation Service<br/>6569/TCP gRPC
    participant OfflineDB as Offline Store<br/>BigQuery/Snowflake<br/>443 HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over MLApp,OfflineDB: Flow 1: Real-Time Feature Retrieval (Online Serving)

    MLApp->>OnlineServer: POST /get-online-features<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (Optional)
    OnlineServer->>Registry: Query feature metadata<br/>gRPC
    Registry-->>OnlineServer: Feature definitions
    OnlineServer->>OnlineDB: Read online features<br/>TLS Optional, Password/mTLS
    OnlineDB-->>OnlineServer: Feature values
    OnlineServer->>Transform: Execute transformations<br/>gRPC
    Transform-->>OnlineServer: Transformed features
    OnlineServer-->>MLApp: JSON/Protobuf response<br/>Feature vectors

    Note over MLApp,OfflineDB: Flow 2: Historical Feature Retrieval (Offline Serving)

    participant TrainingJob as ML Training Job
    participant OfflineServer as Feature Server Offline<br/>8815/TCP HTTP

    TrainingJob->>OfflineServer: POST /get-historical-features<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (Optional)
    OfflineServer->>Registry: Query feature metadata<br/>gRPC
    Registry-->>OfflineServer: Feature definitions
    OfflineServer->>OfflineDB: Query historical data<br/>HTTPS, Cloud IAM Auth
    OfflineDB-->>OfflineServer: Historical features
    OfflineServer-->>TrainingJob: Parquet/CSV response<br/>Training dataset

    Note over MLApp,OfflineDB: Flow 3: Feature Materialization (Offline to Online)

    participant CronJob as CronJob/User

    CronJob->>OnlineServer: POST /materialize<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    OnlineServer->>OfflineDB: Read features from offline store<br/>HTTPS, Cloud IAM
    OfflineDB-->>OnlineServer: Historical features
    OnlineServer->>OnlineDB: Write to online store<br/>TLS Optional, Password
    OnlineDB-->>OnlineServer: Acknowledgment
    OnlineServer-->>CronJob: Materialization complete

    Note over MLApp,OfflineDB: Flow 4: Feature Push (Streaming)

    participant StreamApp as Stream Processing App

    StreamApp->>OnlineServer: POST /push<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    OnlineServer->>OnlineDB: Write features<br/>TLS Optional, Password
    OnlineDB-->>OnlineServer: Acknowledgment
    OnlineServer->>OfflineDB: Optional write to offline<br/>HTTPS, Cloud IAM
    OfflineDB-->>OnlineServer: Acknowledgment
    OnlineServer-->>StreamApp: Push complete
